{"tid":2153014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仇栩欣「警搶電話屈襲擊」 官多番質疑警員口供","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T10:23:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"953ee51033cc8bed84cff6442c0e294a22b80abf","tid":2153014,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/TEGRGDWZO6TUB64DXPDEYFBIMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FTEGRGDWZO6TUB64DXPDEYFBIMI%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=5f804c91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FTEGRGDWZO6TUB64DXPDEYFBIMI%2F&h=fade0ef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/TEGRGDWZO6TUB64DXPDEYFBIMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n仇栩欣「警搶電話屈襲擊」<br />\n官多番質疑警員口供<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月11日北角有「福建幫」與市民衝突，時任社區主任的區議員仇栩欣被指直播街頭情況期間與助理襲警。案件在昨天一周年開審。警員稱有人用粗口和「曱甴」等罵被告，他擔心被告安全，故勸二人離開，其間受襲。辯方指實情是警員因被仇攝錄，憤怒下出手撥或搶仇的電話，事後為掩飾，虛構為被告安全着想而截停，誣告襲警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NqfgF72s29IjGhKOrD6ndCCDHCE=/640x545/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DRWXG2B4NIFTJ6BSGT2MH6PM7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNqfgF72s29IjGhKOrD6ndCCDHCE%3D%2F640x545%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDRWXG2B4NIFTJ6BSGT2MH6PM7Y.jpg&h=08d5bc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仇栩欣被控襲警，昨日到庭聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n報稱受襲的警員許景耀昨供稱，當晚9時巡邏至英皇道商務書局附近，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官何俊堯質疑，書局前方有人群起鬨，「你唔係處理嗰班人，而係去叫兩。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警員指仇栩欣遭截停後情緒失控，激動大叫「走開啦，關你乜事」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0bt0j6-3MVdSJNyaK-KCJj5nfPI=/640x1138/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2H2AP75O24NBYQUHQZE6LCZIOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0bt0j6-3MVdSJNyaK-KCJj5nfPI%3D%2F640x1138%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2H2AP75O24NBYQUHQZE6LCZIOY.jpg&h=303d8034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員許景耀（右）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n箍頸拖到行人路再膝壓<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上播放仇拍攝片段，警員截停仇時，同僚說「喺度偷影我哋」，警員則步近問「影完未」，仇反問：「唔可以影㗎咩？」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指實情是警員不忿被拍攝，故截停被告，撥開或搶仇的手機。兩被告退。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警員承認制服仇時用膝壓身，他稱聽到仇呼喊無法呼吸，故盡快扶起仇坐下。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC103/20"},{"pid":"bd8d12cf632a206335da6504c1a85c5fe5510f3a","tid":2153014,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142357</a>"},{"pid":"6b81a87d55069ad511c07bf9666dae64184c0689","tid":2153014,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:02:48.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64080ea207ebff7bed6792fac9746f37adf022e2","tid":2153014,"uid":16372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"咁後生冇哂頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1125c72d58f59426f23d970b8ec0624a7fb7a6ac","tid":2153014,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:16:38.000Z","msg":"仇栩欣係左右大局 電話講緊"},{"pid":"850d6a2ce6713bd520fe9cb89e3f2a570485391f","tid":2153014,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"隻狗個樣咁撚閪吱"},{"pid":"61e04b2978c672772aa3fadd2dac15ca9709cc05","tid":2153014,"uid":45